text: Roman Ambrožič (born 14 September 1973) is a Slovenian rowing coxswain. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Yugoslavia Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Bled Category:Coxswains (rowing)
